              <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1839/ss:i/p:6">Section 1839(i)(6) of
			 the Social Security Act</cato:entity-ref> (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/42/1395r">
