			 2023</quote>;</text>
					</subparagraph>
          <subparagraph id="id1742E7F0231B44C49454756EB856A273">
            <enum>(B)</enum>
            <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1839/ss:i/p:6/sp:A">subparagraph
			 (A)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking <quote>equal to such amount for 2010; and</quote> and
			 inserting the following: “equal to—</text>
